column2: SELECT TOP # G.ObjID, G.u AS u_mag,                                  G.g AS g_mag, G.r AS r_mag,                                  G.i AS i_mag, G.z AS z_mag,                                  spec.z, spec.zErr         FROM Galaxy AS G         INTO MyDB.photo_redshift          JOIN SpecObjAll AS spec         ON spec.specObjID = G.specObjID          WHERE             spec.z > # AND             spec.z < # AND             spec.zErr < # AND              G.lnlDev_r >  G.lnlExp_r + # AND             G.lnlExp_r > #  AND              (G.flags & (dbo.fPhotoFlags(&&&) + dbo.fPhotoFlags(&&&)                 + dbo.fPhotoFlags(&&&))) > # AND             (G.flags & ( dbo.fPhotoFlags(&&&) +                 dbo.fPhotoFlags(&&&) + dbo.fPhotoFlags(&&&)))                 != dbo.fPhotoFlags(&&&) AND             (G.flags & (dbo.fPhotoFlags(&&&) +                 dbo.fPhotoFlags(&&&))) = # AND             G.petroMag_i > # AND
